item.title: I need help with testscape
item.dc:creator: @ollie123 Ollie123
item.description:
@ollie123 wrote:

What the **** ill tell you now…

click on edit compile.bat and get rid of all the crap in there and replace it with this:

@echo off title [Put Your SErver Name Here] "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.5.0_09\bin\javac.exe" -cp . *.java "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.5.0_09\bin\java.exe" server pause

and make sure u have JDK downloaded heres link:
http://java.sun.com/javase/downloads/index.jsp
